
# Subscription Status

Possible subscription status values.

## Enumeration

`SubscriptionStatus`

## Fields

| Name | Description |
|  --- | --- |
| `DEFAULT_SUBSCRIPTION_STATUS_DO_NOT_USE` |  |
| `PENDING` | The subscription starts in the future. |
| `ACTIVE` | The subscription is active. |
| `CANCELED` | The subscription is canceled. |
